  "dataPolicy": "Official Bundesland-level Schulferien only. School-specific and regional exception dates are excluded.",
  "notes": [
    "endDate is inclusive for app display.",
    "When generating ICS, convert endDate to DTEND as the following day.",
    "The official Schleswig-Holstein page provides the Ferienverordnung 2024/25 bis 2030/31.",
    "The official table states Ferien erster Ferientag / letzter Ferientag.",
    "Bewegliche Ferientage are excluded because §2 states they are set by Schulkonferenz after coordination.",
    "Fallback dates for bewegliche Ferientage are also excluded because they apply only if no agreement is reached.",
    "Island/Hallig exceptions for Sylt, Föhr, Amrum, Helgoland and Halligen are excluded from the default state-level dataset."
  ],
